{"ocr_results":[{"text":"But if the bureau does not approve new overtime, then workers will just not","box":[[87,158],[1424,152],[1424,192],[87,198]]},{"text":"be paid overtime sometimes.","box":[[91,197],[569,198],[569,222],[91,221]]},{"text":"when the 'storming' period begins, administrators and the Party","box":[[248,229],[1369,231],[1369,261],[248,259]]},{"text":"committee call a production meeting (shengchan dahui), a mass rally, where","box":[[94,266],[1405,268],[1405,296],[94,294]]},{"text":"the problem is","box":[[96,305],[344,305],[344,329],[96,329]]},{"text":"s specified--ie. only 5 days left in the period--and that","box":[[330,303],[1334,304],[1334,331],[330,330]]},{"text":"workers should therefore increase their enthusiasm and work hard to overful-","box":[[93,341],[1436,341],[1436,365],[93,365]]},{"text":"fill plans.","box":[[93,374],[325,378],[324,402],[92,398]]},{"text":"The Plant director explains","box":[[323,376],[806,376],[806,400],[323,400]]},{"text":"s the reasons, and the Party and Union","box":[[793,376],[1457,376],[1457,403],[793,403]]},{"text":"has the job of mobilizing the workers' enthusiasm.s","box":[[91,408],[1023,410],[1023,437],[91,435]]},{"text":"Similar meetings take","box":[[1009,412],[1386,412],[1386,439],[1009,439]]},{"text":"place in each shop, department, and production group.","box":[[92,443],[1071,445],[1071,476],[92,474]]},{"text":"There is no regular","box":[[1066,449],[1400,449],[1400,473],[1066,473]]},{"text":"name for all of this, it is just a regular part of industrial practice.","box":[[92,480],[1347,482],[1347,510],[92,508]]},{"text":"Meetings in shops and production groups both at the beginning at the end","box":[[90,515],[1370,516],[1370,546],[90,545]]},{"text":"of the month--at the beginning for announcing tasks and at the end for","box":[[93,550],[1332,552],[1332,579],[93,577]]},{"text":"inspecting progress.","box":[[95,586],[444,589],[444,616],[95,613]]},{"text":"Shop-FloorManagement","box":[[95,657],[468,657],[468,684],[95,684]]},{"text":"(12/27/79,2.5 hrs.)","box":[[506,660],[849,660],[849,683],[506,683]]},{"text":"Hong Kong factories, in which informant has experience as a staff","box":[[252,695],[1401,693],[1401,720],[252,722]]},{"text":"administratora","box":[[96,730],[353,730],[353,753],[96,753]]},{"text":"also have the equivalent of small groups.  A foreman (gongzhang)","box":[[338,727],[1469,729],[1469,759],[338,757]]},{"text":"is theleader of a group of workers on the shop f","box":[[94,762],[955,764],[955,791],[94,789]]},{"text":"floor. Structurally this","box":[[940,764],[1385,763],[1385,790],[940,791]]},{"text":"is similar to China.","box":[[95,798],[486,799],[486,823],[95,822]]},{"text":"But there are no meetings within the group.(","box":[[480,797],[1290,800],[1289,828],[480,824]]},{"text":"Group","box":[[1276,801],[1367,804],[1367,828],[1275,825]]},{"text":"leaders just give orders, don't have discussions.","box":[[96,835],[988,835],[988,859],[96,859]]},{"text":"Also, the foreman is","box":[[999,835],[1350,835],[1350,859],[999,859]]},{"text":"not a production worker, he is a supervisor.","box":[[94,868],[872,869],[872,896],[94,895]]},{"text":"Also, in China, there are many more quotas, f","box":[[252,902],[1044,905],[1044,935],[252,932]]},{"text":"for output, quality;","box":[[1028,905],[1384,907],[1384,934],[1028,932]]},{"text":"original materials, ordering materials, etc.","box":[[97,939],[889,939],[889,966],[97,966]]},{"text":"But in Hong Kong there are","box":[[905,939],[1370,940],[1370,967],[905,966]]},{"text":"noquotas.","box":[[96,977],[313,975],[313,1000],[96,1002]]},{"text":"If you want materials, you just order them.","box":[[306,975],[1069,975],[1069,1002],[306,1002]]},{"text":"Therefore there are","box":[[1104,976],[1439,977],[1439,1001],[1104,1000]]},{"text":"many more records kept at the small group level in China. Materials,","box":[[93,1008],[1317,1007],[1317,1039],[93,1040]]},{"text":"quality, output, waste, working hours, are all recorded and kept by the","box":[[98,1046],[1351,1046],[1351,1073],[98,1073]]},{"text":"group leader himself.1","box":[[93,1081],[505,1074],[506,1105],[94,1112]]},{"text":"But inHongKong","box":[[499,1082],[790,1084],[790,1107],[499,1105]]},{"text":"gtheforeman only records for output,","box":[[776,1081],[1437,1083],[1437,1110],[776,1108]]},{"text":"quality of each worker and hands over to a clerk.","box":[[95,1115],[961,1113],[961,1144],[95,1146]]},{"text":"Small Group Management System:","box":[[255,1151],[786,1153],[786,1180],[255,1178]]},{"text":"Output, quality, original materials,","box":[[817,1152],[1454,1151],[1454,1178],[817,1179]]},{"text":"subsidiary materials, tools, electricity, work hours, attendance, safety.","box":[[95,1184],[1385,1187],[1385,1218],[95,1215]]},{"text":"waste targets are all set for the small","box":[[97,1225],[790,1225],[790,1249],[97,1249]]},{"text":"L group.","box":[[778,1227],[909,1227],[909,1251],[778,1251]]},{"text":"Also productivity rates for","box":[[946,1226],[1421,1226],[1421,1250],[946,1250]]},{"text":"individual machines are set. T","box":[[96,1258],[635,1260],[635,1284],[96,1282]]},{"text":"The group","box":[[623,1260],[790,1262],[789,1287],[622,1285]]},{"text":"0 director is in charge of basic-","box":[[777,1261],[1349,1259],[1349,1283],[777,1285]]},{"text":"level accounting and record-keeping.","box":[[96,1291],[735,1295],[735,1323],[96,1319]]},{"text":"But workers keep their own individual","box":[[766,1297],[1421,1294],[1421,1318],[766,1321]]},{"text":"records, write down their performance after each shift--for output, waste","box":[[97,1328],[1385,1330],[1385,1357],[97,1355]]},{"text":"products (not up to standard), materials use, etc--and hands in to the group","box":[[96,1364],[1439,1364],[1439,1395],[96,1395]]},{"text":"leader every day.","box":[[97,1401],[399,1403],[399,1427],[97,1425]]},{"text":"The leader gives to the shop office, who staff sums","box":[[431,1402],[1336,1402],[1336,1429],[431,1429]]},{"text":"sup","box":[[1323,1405],[1386,1405],[1386,1430],[1323,1430]]},{"text":"and turns over the different figures to the departments concerned.","box":[[94,1434],[1270,1435],[1270,1465],[94,1464]]},{"text":"'Original","box":[[1254,1434],[1457,1436],[1457,1463],[1254,1461]]},{"text":"records' (yuanshi jilu) is the name applied to these cards kept by workers.","box":[[96,1470],[1420,1472],[1420,1502],[96,1500]]},{"text":"It is very easy for the group leader to check to see if these records are","box":[[95,1504],[1387,1505],[1387,1535],[95,1534]]},{"text":"false.","box":[[101,1543],[216,1543],[216,1564],[101,1564]]},{"text":"Helooks at the","box":[[234,1540],[507,1542],[507,1567],[234,1564]]},{"text":"erecord and if it doesn't make sense he can verify","box":[[497,1540],[1385,1542],[1385,1570],[497,1567]]},{"text":"quicklybygoingaround","box":[[99,1578],[508,1578],[508,1605],[99,1605]]},{"text":"ato check.This is because the group leader knows","box":[[493,1577],[1387,1579],[1387,1605],[493,1603]]},{"text":"his workers well, knows whether they are good or bad workers, and also","box":[[94,1610],[1334,1611],[1334,1642],[94,1641]]},{"text":"works right alongside them all day long.","box":[[96,1646],[804,1649],[804,1676],[96,1673]]},{"text":"So its a self-reporting system,","box":[[837,1647],[1384,1650],[1384,1677],[836,1674]]},{"text":"butgiventhenatureofthesmallc","box":[[97,1686],[707,1686],[707,1709],[97,1709]]},{"text":"group，i","box":[[695,1687],[830,1687],[830,1711],[695,1711]]},{"text":"its hard to cheat.","box":[[819,1685],[1136,1685],[1136,1709],[819,1709]]},{"text":"The group leader receives these original records and makes 'small","box":[[257,1718],[1405,1717],[1405,1744],[257,1745]]},{"text":"group records' (xiaozu jilu).","box":[[95,1755],[644,1751],[644,1782],[95,1785]]},{"text":"His job is to verify， add together and sand","box":[[641,1753],[1407,1754],[1407,1782],[641,1781]]},{"text":"up to the shop.","box":[[96,1791],[401,1789],[401,1817],[96,1819]]},{"text":"He does this the first thing every morning, before the shift.","box":[[390,1790],[1474,1790],[1474,1820],[390,1820]]},{"text":"It takes only about l5 minutes, and the calculations are very simple.","box":[[95,1823],[1341,1826],[1341,1855],[95,1852]]},{"text":"He","box":[[1350,1830],[1388,1830],[1388,1853],[1350,1853]]},{"text":"also has to compare the performance of workers.If there are problems,","box":[[97,1859],[1351,1863],[1351,1890],[97,1886]]},{"text":"he must go to the worker and find out the cause, and do remedial training","box":[[93,1890],[1389,1895],[1389,1926],[93,1921]]},{"text":"or education of lax workers.","box":[[94,1928],[589,1928],[589,1959],[94,1959]]},{"text":"The small group records are handed over to the shop director,","box":[[254,1964],[1340,1969],[1340,1999],[254,1994]]},{"text":"if there is no section in between shop and small g","box":[[95,2000],[976,2002],[976,2032],[95,2030]]},{"text":"group","box":[[962,2006],[1057,2006],[1057,2030],[962,2030]]},{"text":"0 levels.","box":[[1044,2005],[1236,2005],[1236,2029],[1044,2029]]},{"text":"Actually","box":[[1228,2005],[1369,2007],[1369,2031],[1228,2029]]},{"text":"the records go to the shop statistician (tongji, jihua yuan) or to·the","box":[[98,2038],[1336,2041],[1336,2068],[98,2065]]},{"text":"shop planning workers.","box":[[99,2076],[508,2076],[508,2100],[99,2100]]},{"text":"These shop offices","box":[[520,2074],[846,2075],[846,2102],[520,2101]]},{"text":"6filloutdailyproduction reports","box":[[832,2075],[1441,2076],[1441,2103],[831,2102]]},{"text":"basedon small group records.","box":[[95,2110],[638,2113],[638,2138],[95,2134]]},{"text":"These daily production reports (shengchan","box":[[642,2111],[1373,2112],[1373,2140],[642,2139]]},{"text":"-10-","box":[[770,2164],[839,2164],[839,2193],[770,2193]]}],"dimensions":{"height":2220,"width":1657}}